description:
Agents

True love. Fashion forward fascism. Double agent--love/murder. Science via crime via COPRA. Origin story: DY DY.

Copra is a team of mercenary weirdos who have amassed a long string of enemies. Adjusting our focus on each key villain, we now turn our attention to: DY DY in "Agents".

Collects Copra #1, Copra #8, and Copra #9.
